Life is a domino effect

One small action leads to another

Which slowly builds you up and

occasionally knocks you down!

And so are those budding Ideas!

Don't ever doubt that small single thought that can

trigger an unstoppable chain of events

that gain momentum with increasing force

at the end of which lies something fruitful

or even revolutionary!

so embrace the domino effect and keep on building, until one day

you get to witness the magic of your worthwhile contributions!

About

Innovations for a Better Tomorrow (IBeTo) is a technical innovations competition hosted by Govt. Model Engineering College, Kochi as part of the annual national level technical symposium, Excel 2020. IBeTo is a nationwide initiative that provides a platform that allows young innovative minds to demonstrate how their ideas can help make a better tomorrow.

Innovations for a Better Tomorrow (IBeTo) is the flagship event of EXCEL. It is a national level pursuit for socially relevant and technologically innovative ideas with the potential to trigger the next big social change. IBeTo gives the right platform and mentorship to launch the most technically innovative and revolutionary ideas and to develop them into a final product.

Event Format

This is the event format for Ibeto 2020

IDEATE

PHASE I

Participants will submit their ideas and their choice of problem statement with solution. 60 teams will be shortlisted and asked to send a detailed abstract.

CREATE

PHASE II

20 teams shortlisted into the quarterfinals will be asked to send in their project plans and assigned mentors to whom the teams are to report to.

SHOWCASE

PHASE III

20 teams shortlisted into the quarterfinals will be asked to send in their project plans and assigned mentors to whom the teams are to report to.
